    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, honest mint-condition car that presents about as well as a used vehicle can. It runs and drives beautifully, shows extremely minimal wear inside and out, and has clearly been very well cared for. The interior is especially tidy, the exterior has a strong, clean appearance, and overall it feels like a standout example. If you want a used car that needs no excuses and should impress in person, this is the kind of vehicle to come see.",
      "price": 46950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
