    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an affordable price, this vehicle is a smart choice for a buyer who values practicality over perfection. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking a low-cost daily driver, backup vehicle, or project opportunity. A straightforward, budget-conscious offering with real usability and strong value for the money.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great chance to grab something budget-friendly with plenty of potential. It\u2019s being sold as-is and shows its age, but for the right buyer it could make a practical runabout, a fixer-upper, or a handy spare vehicle. If you like getting good value and don\u2019t mind giving a car a bit of TLC, this one could be well worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest project with solid enthusiast potential. This car still delivers the kind of mechanical feel that makes it worth saving: engine fires up, drivetrain pulls, and the chassis has the planted, connected character you want in a usable fixer-upper. It\u2019s not a cosmetic queen and will need attention, but for someone who appreciates a machine with good bones, this is a compelling entry point into ownership without stretching into cleaner-car money. Great candidate for a budget driver build, weekend wrenching, or parts-compatible restoration.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Rough around the edges, but priced to move. Cheap entry, no fluff. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough, this car has the kind of personality you can\u2019t fake\u2014honest, seasoned, and ready for its next chapter. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates a vehicle with story, presence, and plenty of life to give in the right hands. Whether you need an inexpensive runabout, a project with charm, or something with old-school character that stands apart from the ordinary, this one brings that rugged appeal in spades. Priced to move and full of potential.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers an affordable way into dependable transportation. Best suited for buyers who value practicality and price over cosmetics, this car presents a strong opportunity as a commuter, starter vehicle, or backup runabout. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering real utility and value.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t a showroom piece, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who wants cheap transport, a handy backup vehicle, or a solid little project. It has character, it\u2019s priced to sell, and for the money there\u2019s real value here. If you\u2019re practical and don\u2019t mind something a bit rough around the edges, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Strong-running project with great bones and real enthusiast potential. The powertrain pulls cleanly, chassis feels planted, and it presents as a worthwhile platform for someone who appreciates a driver-focused setup. Cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. A smart buy for a budget-minded owner wanting usable transportation now with room to sort and improve over time.",
